  "excerpt": "<p>Thanksgiving is two weeks from today! It’s been my holiday to cook for over ten years, but this year we are heading to my aunt’s house instead. I’ll miss cooking everything, but I’ll still enjoy my favorite meal of the year- and this year I’ll get to actually see the Philly Thanksgiving Day Parade, which [&hellip;]</p>\n",
  "content": "<p>Thanksgiving is two weeks from today! It’s been my holiday to cook for over ten years, but this year we are heading to my aunt’s house instead. I’ll miss cooking everything, but I’ll still enjoy my favorite meal of the year- and this year I’ll get to actually see the Philly Thanksgiving Day Parade, which is pretty awesome! Whatever you are doing for the holiday, there is something on this shopping list that would make your family gathering even better!</p>\n<p>I really love the Gobble Til You Wobble shirt! So cute. All these items would make a great addition to Thanksgiving, though! <strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyODAwMDA3Mg/thanksgiving-etsy-faves\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Shop the original treasury here</a></strong>, or click on the links to each item below!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/214685962/thanksgiving-banners-thankful-banner?ref=tre-2728000072-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Banner Cheer Jr</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/247872481/rustic-pumpkin-fall-decor-thanksgiving?ref=tre-2728000072-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cedar and Sea</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/164826404/thanksgiving-wreaths-fall-wreaths?ref=tre-2728000072-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Two Inspire You</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/105862051/large-turkey-pumpkin-pokes-thanksgiving?ref=tre-2728000072-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Woodndoodads</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/254652813/thankful-shirt-with-glitter-accent?ref=tre-2728000072-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">J & A Apparel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/85543277/thanksgiving-dog-collar-1-inch-wide?ref=tre-2728000072-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Canine Design</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/79745228/pumpkin-earrings-fall-festive-jewelry?ref=tre-2728000072-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Pinking-Edge Designs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/206970059/thanksgiving-photo-booth-props?ref=tre-2728000072-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Paper Built Shop</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/247775179/fall-mason-jars-fall-centerpieces-autumn?ref=tre-2728000072-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">My Heart By Hand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/167740101/thanksgiving-cookies-turkey-cookies?ref=tre-2728000072-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rollin’ In Dough</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/251967527/thanksgiving-headband-thanksgiving-baby?ref=tre-2728000072-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Pink Pineapple Couture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/244591925/thanksgiving-place-cards-set-of-12-food?ref=tre-2728000072-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Decorate Your Big Day</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/243265261/give-thanks-sign-thanksgiving-sign-give?ref=tre-2728000072-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sweet Elodie Grace</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/204339562/baby-girl-thanksgiving-outfit-newborn?ref=tre-2728000072-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Childish Dreams</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/248954526/funny-thanksgiving-shirt-gobble-til-you?ref=tre-2728000072-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Shirt Candy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/252034837/thanksgiving-turkey-cake-pops-festive?ref=tre-2728000072-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Mad Platter Kitchen</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Which Thanksgiving item is your favorite? What are your plans for the holiday?</p>\n",
